[Episode 16]

10
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:59,520
You want to ruin me.

11
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,520
Then I won't let you walk away safe!

12
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:03,800
Let's go down together.

13
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,560
And you shareholders,

14
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,200
