16
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,360
None of you will get away!

17
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,976
Mr. Fang,

18
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,216
what you're doing now

19
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,960
won't solve anything.

20
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:21,120
You'll only push yourself to the edge.

21
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,136
You don't want to
spend the rest of your life

22
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,400
