23
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,736
I can put the gun down.

24
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,136
But you have to reinstate my position.

25
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,496
Otherwise,

26
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:37,800
I'll take someone down
with me even if I die!

27
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:43,520
What a loser.

28
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,080
Still wants to drag someone down
even in death.

29
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,896
That scheming woman An Ning.

30
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,096
[Equity Transfer Agreement]
signed an Equity Transfer Agreement.

31
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,256
We can't use force against her anymore.

32
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,696
Go coax her.

33
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,537
Maybe if she softens up,

34
00:01:58,561 --> 00:02:00,520
we can trick her out of her shares.

35
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,640
Mom.

36
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,256
I was cuckolded by my own dad.

37
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,080
I'm in no mood to care about this.

38
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,296
You think I am, huh?

39
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,920
You're not the only one
who got betrayed.

40
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,616
The shares are what matter now.

41
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:16,296
If we don't seize her shares soon,

42
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,016
