43
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,816
And you're still
thinking about that nonsense?

44
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,417
This... this...

45
00:02:20,441 --> 00:02:22,040
Just think carefully.

46
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,256
Here's the current
stock price of the group.

47
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,816
You forced the Fang family out
of the group.

48
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,896
It did serve as a warning.

49
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,680
Many shareholders
act obedient out of fear.

50
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,440
But that doesn't mean
they truly accept it.

51
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,360
Shareholders only care about profit.

52
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,456
As long as the money keeps coming in,

53
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,800
they don't care what you do.

54
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,376
But the Fang family

55
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,896
will never let this go.

56
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,920
The Fang family is already cornered.

57
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,616
If they dare to bare their teeth again,

58
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,960
then hit back hard.

59
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,560
Why are you here?

60
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,656
You're my wife.

61
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,576
Is there a problem with me

62
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,600
coming to see you?

63
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:02,880
Also,

64
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,216
why is he here?

65
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,057
What...

66
00:03:06,081 --> 00:03:07,816
What exactly are you trying to do?

67
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,936
Huo Xiao is a director of the group.

68
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,240
We were just discussing work.

69
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,920
Discussing work?

70
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,960
Is that what you call discussing work?

71
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,760
Ti Cha.

72
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,496
Calm down.

73
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:22,496
Don't do anything you'll regret.

74
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,497
What a joke.

75
00:03:23,521 --> 00:03:24,816
I'm talking to An Ning.

76
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,896
What's it got to do with you?

77
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:28,256
Besides, I haven't even asked you yet.

78
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,176
What are you doing in my wife's office

79
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,456
in broad daylight?

80
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,480
Huh?

81
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,800
You must have heard about

82
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,480
that Fang guy being fired from the group

83
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,120
and holding the board at gunpoint.

84
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:44,320
The Chairman and I
were discussing prevention plans.

85
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,760
An Ning,

86
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,600
is what he said true?

87
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,336
Whether it's true or not,

88
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,616
you'll know if you go ask yourself.

89
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:54,080
You shameless woman,
daring to give me attitude.

90
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,800
Fine, for the sake of the shares,

91
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,760
I'll let it slide this time.

92
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,817
Ning,

93
00:04:03,841 --> 00:04:04,936
I was wrong

94
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,960
