95
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,040
I... I apologize to you.

96
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,297
No need.

97
00:04:10,321 --> 00:04:11,736
Just stop using those nasty thoughts

98
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,920
to judge others.

99
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,016
If there's nothing else,

100
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,376
please leave.

101
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,400
I...

102
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:20,880
I... I'll eave here.

103
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,296
He should be the one to leave.

104
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,560
Huo Xiao has no right to
even stand here.

105
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,680
Huo Xiao, let me tell you.

106
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,136
Me and Ning

107
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,560
are still married.

108
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,480
And you'll always be a home wrecker.

109
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,240
Ning.

110
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,497
In the past,

111
00:04:39,521 --> 00:04:40,696
it was all my fault.

112
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,577
I promise you

113
00:04:41,601 --> 00:04:42,696
I'll change and make things right.

114
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,536
Look.

115
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,337
I

116
00:04:44,361 --> 00:04:45,816
Bought you your favorite flowers

117
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:48,136
and booked a table
at your favorite restaurant.

118
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,416
Plus

119
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:51,456
the tickets to your favorite concert.

120
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,457
That's enough.

121
00:04:52,481 --> 00:04:53,896
This is Longxing Group.

122
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,240
I still have a meeting to attend.

123
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,560
This...

124
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,776
An Ning used to fall for that easily.

125
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,416
Just a little gesture,

126
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,240
and she'd give me whatever I asked for.

127
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,640
Huo Xiao.

128
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,696
If you want to compete,

129
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,040
then let's see who's better.

130
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,056
Let's see

131
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,160
who ends up embarrassed.

132
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,856
Wait, wait.

133
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:34,040
Don't lose your temper, seriously.

134
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,160
You, you, you...

135
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,056
Dad.

136
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,096
Please don't be angry.

137
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,816
I have a way to deal with
that sneaky woman.

138
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,120
What other way?

139
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,376
This time I used every connection I have.

140
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,576
Paid a huge price for it.

141
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,096
Barely managed to get bailed out.

142
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,176
If she doesn't fall,

143
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:31,897
our family

144
00:06:31,921 --> 00:06:33,080
will never rise again.

145
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:36,760
Though we can't
take her spot as chairman,

146
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,897
we can

147
00:06:37,921 --> 00:06:39,480
approach this from another angle.

148
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,560
Good.

149
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:53,817
Dear,

150
00:06:53,841 --> 00:06:54,880
look at her.

151
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,720
Look.

152
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,976
Sly woman, I knew you would cheat.

153
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,416
How could you do something
so disgraceful?

154
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:09,320
You've completely humiliated our family.

155
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,976
Don't you think

156
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,320
you owe us an explanation?

157
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,920
Is that all?

158
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,297
Anything else?

159
00:07:24,321 --> 00:07:25,480
Is that not enough?

160
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:29,056
How many shameless things have you done?

161
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,136
Our family must've
run out of luck ages ago

162
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:33,056
to marry
such a shameless daughter-in-law.

163
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,576
Can't you see

164
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,896
this is a cheap frame-up?

165
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,720
These are just
fake computer-generated photos.

166
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,776
If I wanted to,

167
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,856
I could replace the face in the photos

168
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,880
with anyone's.

169
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,696
You shameless woman.

170
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,457
Still trying to talk your way out of it?

171
00:07:44,481 --> 00:07:45,640
I'll beat you!

172
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,257
An Ning!

173
00:07:48,281 --> 00:07:49,816
You're accusing your own family

174
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,536
without reason.

175
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,640
If you want an explanation,

176
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,296
go talk to whoever
gave you those photos.

177
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,896
Don't think we don't know about

178
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,976
the shameful things you've done.

179
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,456
If this gets out,
it'll damage the company's image.

180
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,936
You must resign!

181
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,400
You don't need to worry about that.

182
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,120
I'll give you an explanation for this today.

183
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,240
Dear, look at her.

184
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,240
Chairman An.

185
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,680
What's really going on here?

186
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,496
You must give the board an explanation.

187
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,696
As a responsible group

188
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,056
with a sense of duty,

189
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,696
Longxing Group will never tolerate

190
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,120
such unfounded slander!

191
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:35,096
As the group's main shareholder,

192
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,256
I'm not even rushing this.

193
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,376
So why are you all panicking?

194
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,696
Before figuring out the truth,

195
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,176
you're already desperate to cut ties.

196
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,280
Isn't that exactly what the person
behind this wants?

197
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,936
If we don't find who's pulling the strings,

198
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,616
whoever takes that chairman seat

199
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,680
won't have it easy.

200
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,536
Chairman An,

201
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,056
the board really can't be accused of

202
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,696
not giving you a chance now.

203
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:14,216
I'm here to handle
the resignation procedures.

204
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,456
The process isn't done yet,

205
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,240
so I can't leave for now.

206
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,440
Luckily I got to catch this drama unfold.

207
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:26,656
Otherwise I'd have missed
my best friend's brilliant move.

208
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,520
That would've been such a shame.

209
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,296
I'm really curious.

210
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:37,080
With such a huge scandal
hanging over you,

211
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,720
the whole group's about to sink with you.

212
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,560
How do you plan to make a comeback now?

213
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,136
- Chairman An.
- Make way, please.

214
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,896
Chairman An, can we get a comment?

215
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:45,577
Stop filming, stop filming!

216
00:09:45,601 --> 00:09:46,881
- Chairman An.
- No more filming!

217
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,457
Chairman An!

218
00:09:48,481 --> 00:09:49,656
What do you want to say

219
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,656
about this incident?

220
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:51,097
- Yeah.
- Exactly.

221
00:09:51,121 --> 00:09:52,536
Exactly, any comment on this incident?

222
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,976
- About this incident...
- Please look at the camera.

223
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,616
Will there be any further impact?

224
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,016
Please answer our question.

225
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,256
- Please say something.
- Yeah, give us an answer.

226
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,280
Exactly, please respond directly
to our question.

227
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,960
You must be very proud now, right?

228
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,840
The woman in that video
has a mole on her left shoulder.

229
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,880
But I don't.

230
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,816
She's got two studs on her right ear.

231
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,016
And I don't wear any.

232
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,456
I know spreading rumors is easy,
but clearing them isn't.

233
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,896
Many people only care about
clicks and sensationalism,

234
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,440
not the truth.

235
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,936
I'm not just explaining this

236
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,760
to prove my innocence.

237
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,656
I also want to ask one thing.

238
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,600
Can't you see how shoddy

239
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,400
this computer-generated video is?

240
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,440
Do you think you can fool everyone

241
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,936
with just a few vague words

242
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,600
to prove the video is fake?

243
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,320
Then do you think

244
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,120
it's real?

245
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,136
Stop filming, all of you, stop!

246
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:54,576
Stop filming!

247
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,600
An Ning, how dare you!

248
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,016
It's fake, completely fake!

249
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,176
Of course it's fake.

250
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,536
I was just using you as an example.

251
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,736
After all,

252
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:05,120
you're the one behind all of this.

253
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,776
I've already found
the original IP address of this video

254
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:13,560
and the on-site surveillance footage.

255
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,960
Fang Yao,
do you have anything else to say?

256
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,417
Miss Fang,

257
00:11:18,441 --> 00:11:19,456
is any of this real?

258
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,640
Could you please explain?

259
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,080
An Ning, I...

260
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,920
You don't have to explain it to me.

261
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,800
You should explain it to the police.

262
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,096
Even if the video's fake,

263
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,456
flirting with

264
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,696
the Inspector as a married woman

265
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,000
is totally true.

266
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,536
Nonsense!

267
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,936
You think you know my wife

268
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,320
better than I do?

269
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,096
Honey.

270
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,120
Fang Yao,

271
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,360
you're a woman too.

272
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,497
Don't you know

273
00:11:49,521 --> 00:11:51,696
how harmful

274
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,416
these rumors are once they spread?

275
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,456
They can even

276
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:57,200
destroy her whole life.

277
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,560
I don't care at all.

278
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,376
I just want you gone!

279
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,400
Yao.

